                            <div class="mil-text-center">
                                <h2 class="mil-mb-30 mil-up">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                                <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft mil-mb-60 mil-up">Everything you need to know about Project Management Subscription</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mil-accordion">
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>How does the no upfront payment work?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                        <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft">You don't pay anything before each construction milestone. Payments are made only after you have inspected and approved the completed milestone. This ensures quality and protects your investment.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>What is construction finance credit?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                        <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft">Construction finance credit is available to help you fund your project. We partner with financial institutions to provide affordable financing options for qualified subscribers.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>How do you ensure quality of building materials?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-content">
                                        <p class="mil-text-m mil-soft">We have a strict quality assurance process for all building materials. Our team verifies material quality before purchase and delivery to ensure only the best materials are used in your project.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mil-accordion-group mil-up">
                                    <div class="mil-accordion-menu">
                                        <h5>Are the contractors and artisans pre-qualified?</h5>
                                        <div class="mil-accordion-icon"><i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i></div>
